                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/files/home/carousel/image-02.webp"
                     alt="1687301198446-L.png"
                     width="1411"
                     height="228"
                     style="
                width: 1573px;
                height: 228px;
                object-fit: cover;
                object-position: 50% 50%;
              "
                     fetchpriority="high" />
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <p class="fs-5">
                        <span style="font-size: 21px">100% НАТУРАЛНА ГРИЖА ЗА КОЖАТА</span>
                    </p>
                    <h2 class="h2">
                        РЪЧНО ИЗРАБОТЕНА<br />
                        С ЛЮБО
                    </h2>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="~/files/home/carousel/image-03.webp"
                     alt="IMG_20230907_190239.png"
                     width="1411"
                     height="228"
                     style="
                width: 1573px;
                height: 228px;
                object-fit: cover;
                object-position: 50% 50%;
              "
                     fetchpriority="high" />
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h2 class="h2">НЕЖНИ ФОРМУЛИ</h2>

                    <p class="fs-5">
                        СЪСТАВКИ ОТ БЪЛГАРИЯ И С БИО ПРОЗХОД. БЕЗ АЛКОХОЛ. СЪЗДАДЕНИ ДА
